    public class MultipleChoiceExpandableListAdapterImplementation<GroupType,ChildType>
extends AbstractSelectableExpandableListAdapter<GroupType,ChildType>
implements MultipleChoiceExpandableListAdapter<GroupType,ChildType>
    An adapter, whose underlying data is managed as a list of arbitrary group and child items, of which multiple items can be selected at once. Such an adapter's purpose is to provide the underlying data for visualization using a ExpandableListView widget.
    Since:
    0.1.0
